extends ../layout/main

block content
  section.contact
    .contact__container.container
      h2.heading-primary.contact__heading Let's Connect
      p.paragraph.paragraph--abstract.contact__abstract
        | Thank you for checking out my website 🙏. If you have any questions, feel free to shoot me an email 📧. I'll get back to you as soon as I can 🙂

      .contact__form-container
        form.form.form-contact
          +formInput('text', 'Name', 'name', 'form-contact__name', true)
          +formInput('text', 'Company', 'company', 'form-contact__company', false)
          +formInput('tel', 'Phone', 'phone', 'form-contact__phone')
          +formInput('email', 'Email', 'email', 'form-contact__email', true)
          +formInput('text', 'Subject', 'subject', 'form-contact__subject', true)
          +formTextarea('Message', 'message', 'form-contact__message', true)

          .form__group.form__group--btn.form-contact__btn
            button.btn.btn--primary(type="submit") Submit
            button.btn(type="button") Clear

      .contact__artwork-container
        img.contact__artwork(src="/src/img/color-themes/green/get-in-touch.svg")/